title: Cafe 21 at Info Lab
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Beer/Wine, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. University eatery that's open to all. Offers a daytime menu with vegetarian, vegan, and 1 to 2 fish dishes - ranges from sandwich to main meals. Spacious 4th floor space with views, accessible by lift. Drinks til 4:30pm.
